  "common_mistakes": [
    "Going DOWN from the bottomless hole ledge (room 30) - leads to Hell and death",
    "Carrying too many items into quicksand (room 26) - cannot swim out if too heavy",
    "Jumping across the chasm with fire bricks - too heavy, you fall and die",
    "Forgetting to bring mud to the bee room - cannot get the honey without it",
    "Not lighting the lamp before going underground - cannot see in dark areas",
    "Wasting lamp turns - use UNLIGHT LAMP when in lit areas to conserve the 125-turn limit",
    "Going N/S/W in the forest (room 11) - all loop back, only EAST progresses",
    "Not reading the spider web in room 2 - misses the AWAY magic word",
    "Trying to swim at the lake - the sign says no swimming and you cannot",
    "Going SOUTH, WEST, or DOWN in Limbo (room 33) - leads to Hell. Only EAST saves you",
